{"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error CS0255\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"CS0255\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"CS0255\"\nms.assetid: b45f5d5a-1923-4fe1-a858-e5ef5590a108\n---\n# Compiler Error CS0255\nstackalloc may not be used in a catch or finally block  \n  \n The [stackalloc](../../csharp/language-reference/keywords/stackalloc.md) keyword may not be used in a [catch](../../csharp/language-reference/keywords/try-catch.md) or [finally](../../csharp/language-reference/keywords/try-catch-finally.md) block. For more information, see [Exceptions and Exception Handling](../../csharp/programming-guide/exceptions/index.md).  \n  \n The following sample generates CS0255:  \n  \n```csharp  \n// CS0255.cs  \n// compile with: /unsafe  \nusing System;  \n  \npublic class TestTryFinally  \n{  \n   public static unsafe void Test()  \n   {  \n      int i = 123;  \n      string s = \"Some string\";  \n      object o = s;  \n  \n      try  \n      {  \n         // Conversion is not valid; o contains a string not an int  \n         i = (int) o;  \n      }  \n  \n      finally  \n      {  \n         Console.Write(\"i = {0}\", i);  \n         int* fib = stackalloc int[100];   // CS0255  \n      }  \n   }  \n  \n   public static void Main()  \n   {  \n   }  \n}  \n```\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,165],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"Compiler Error CS0255\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"CS0255\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"CS0255\"\nms.assetid: b45f5d5a-1923-4fe1-a858-e5ef5590a108","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0255","nodes":[{"pos":[0,21],"content":"Compiler Error CS0255","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0255","pos":[0,21]}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[172,193],"content":"Compiler Error CS0255","linkify":"Compiler Error CS0255","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0255","pos":[0,21]}]},{"content":"stackalloc may not be used in a catch or finally block","pos":[194,248]},{"content":"The <bpt id